text: Ah Ah Ah is a song by American rapper DreamDoll and singer Fivio Foreign. The song was released July 10, 2020. == Background == The song is about DreamDoll working in The Bronx. Magazine LA Weekly thought her singing style was good. == Chart performance == The song ranked number 23 on the Billboard Sales chart for two weeks. == References == Category:2020 songs Category:Rap songs
title: Ah Ah Ah (song)
